------------------------------------------------------------------------------
PttXP Changelog
------------------------------------------------------------------------------

PttXP 0.1.5 (October 10, 2010):

	Bugs fixed:
	* Fix delete_header macro
	* In crosspost mode, retry for 5 times if login failed.

	Features added:
	* crosspost is now moved to another thread, prevent GUI from hanging

PttXP 0.1.3 (September 26th, 2010):

	Bugs fixed:
	* Fix go_board macro

PttXP 0.1.2 (September 21th, 2010):

	Bugs fixed:
	* Fix login error
	* Fix newline character under windows

	Features added:
	* delete post header 

PttXP 0.1.1 (September 11th, 2010):

	* Initial release
